textBox.richText: some people draw like i write....

So a friend who was going cross country from San Diego, stopped by into Manhattan to see me!. I’m not going to lie and say I know my maps very well. I did know San Diego was in California, and where California is, but other than that, I was lost. So my friend decided to show me where she lived. It’s a good thing she’s a photographer, and not an artist....
A Photographer’s version of the US
